{"tid":1103033,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[人美心美] IZ*ONE偷偷抹淚！見面會遇到到坐輪椅來的小粉絲","createTime":"2019-04-12T06:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T10:16:56.000Z","uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b6bc3197ef1171a242b593c132877df336f111fd","tid":1103033,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"4月7日IZ*ONE在首爾舉辦粉絲簽名會時，出現了一位略顯獨特的小粉絲。 從背面看應該是個小女孩，坐在輪椅上和成員們一一互動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_187e15911c78b859052607d763fe6c64/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-04-11/115677-723851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_187e15911c78b859052607d763fe6c64%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-04-11%2F115677-723851.jpg&h=0387a243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據當時在場的粉絲透露，因為女孩身體不便，是由父親代為參加見面會的招募，帶著小孩走了6小時的路才來到現場。 雖然在後面看不到小女孩的表情，但看到喜歡的姐姐們就在面前一定很開心吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_411e1096aa05468beb1dcb31d0a6afc2/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-04-11/115677-723847.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_411e1096aa05468beb1dcb31d0a6afc2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-04-11%2F115677-723847.jpg&h=ac04c812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李彩演一直帶著開心的笑容跟她說話，還不時對她豎起大拇指，最後和她拉勾勾：<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1f29bb990a81286a43dcbaca0e26e700/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-04-11/115677-723854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1f29bb990a81286a43dcbaca0e26e700%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-04-11%2F115677-723854.jpg&h=1ae07c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一直到小粉絲移動到下一位成員的位置，李彩演才讓淚水流下來，看來她也因為小粉絲而受到不少感動呢T^T<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_fda96a8a422b3eebb075a334f7b1e635/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-04-11/115677-723852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_fda96a8a422b3eebb075a334f7b1e635%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-04-11%2F115677-723852.jpg&h=5f2c7258&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f2ee30346424758d90f664106a7f7f0399b6152","tid":1103033,"uid":46435,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:54:50.000Z","msg":"IZONE小姐姐們真係個好好既榜樣 覺得自己無飯錯人好能想哭.."},{"pid":"1a402403de9218d9a2b39c40e2a6a216a5c471f6","tid":1103033,"uid":174100,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"彩演<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />演"},{"pid":"0f6fa032e3e1327dd2b6e7d223613235d5ea9241","tid":1103033,"uid":2781,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:58:43.000Z","msg":"佢真係喊緊?似係忍唔住笑咁嘅"},{"pid":"9a7128720d34bf8964293d662bcf916d41dd7caa","tid":1103033,"uid":43061,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"人不美心美<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhDK4WZaepo&amp;t=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJhDK4WZaepo%26t%3D&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8KGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=ce7fe54f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhDK4WZaepo&amp;t=</a><br />\n個個都對個妹妹勁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5431889a8fe7f85a181bc9794199bfef755bde45","tid":1103033,"uid":133988,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAFb1vf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAFb1vf.gif&h=8dcf6f99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62482089a3aecd93816b96295b4290210217c9bc","tid":1103033,"uid":85591,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5431889a8fe7f85a181bc9794199bfef755bde45","tid":1103033,"uid":133988,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAFb1vf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt